pageTitle: Itinerary for Saturday, May 12, 2018 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Québec, Quebec

11:30 a.m. The Prime Minister will participate in the inauguration of the new Québec Armoury.

Québec Armoury
805, avenue Wilfrid-Laurier Ouest

Notes to media:

    • Open coverage
    • Media are asked to arrive no later than 10:30 a.m. at the door on l’avenue George V.

Media Appearances

9:09 a.m. An interview with the Prime Minister will air on Salut Bonjour Week-end, TVA.
